Moving in the Elevator
Elevator moves in the requested direction.

Stops at intermediate floors if there are requests in the same direction.

Elevator arrives at the destination floor, doors open.

User exits, and the elevator continues to the next request.

3️⃣ Handling Emergency
User presses Emergency Stop inside the elevator.

Elevator stops immediately.

An alert is sent to the building monitoring system.

Technician intervention is required.

4️⃣ Maintenance Mode
Technician sets the elevator to maintenance mode.

The elevator stops accepting new requests.

Passengers inside are moved to the nearest floor and asked to exit.